{"tid":568295,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"俾錢買 Game 仲要課金！EA 或失 Star Wars 遊戲發行權！","createTime":"2018-02-21T15:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T02:34:39.000Z","uid":1886,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5ff5258ec15ff6b0615164c8ff4453de7d70289c","tid":568295,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:51:35.000Z","msg":"Disney 擁有《Star War》版權，於 2013 年授權 EA 發行遊戲，期間推出了多款遊戲作品，但單以《Star Wars Battlefront》及《Star Wars Battlefront 2》來說，每次推出都可以引來激烈劣評，例如上年的《Star Wars Battlefront 2》，就因為一眾玩家對課金制度的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n最近有消息傳出，有可能撤銷 EA 針對 Star War 遊戲的發行權，不過若然撤銷 EA 的遊戲發行權，旗下多款遊戲幾可肯定會受影響，包括手遊及主機遊戲，投入資金將一去不返。至於接手問題，相信 Ubisoft、Activision 等廠商均願意接手。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://pc3mag.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/STAR-WAR20022018-768x402.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2FSTAR-WAR20022018-768x402.jpg&h=6ef4a1c9&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://pc3mag.com/ea-lost-star-war-distribution-right/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fea-lost-star-war-distribution-right%2F&d=%2FaD7KDOFmFMMeKtofmtbWr5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=6f7bf245\" target=\"_blank\">http://pc3mag.com/ea-lost-star-war-distribution-right/</a>"},{"pid":"1072107bb53e62b8f4b325bc939a088c46018b6f","tid":568295,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:52:14.000Z","msg":"《Star War》電影不知不覺已經上映了三集，根據原先的計劃，仍有三集將於未來三年上映，包括兩集外傳及一集正傳，如果以「搵銀」角度而言，剩下三年時間製造熱潮，不算多也不算少，但電影及遊戲迴響都不似預期，實在難以令 Disney 感到滿意。"},{"pid":"1acd3451ff5ca724bf691230f31970daf4ac8918","tid":568295,"uid":7237,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:55:22.000Z","msg":"Ubi接手嘅話我寧願佢唔撤銷畀返EA搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a40a883e67a91f753c12335905f43f0a5bb775","tid":568295,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1acd3